{"tid":1429194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方幾時拘捕幻彩詠香江負責人","createTime":"2019-08-07T12:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:14:12.000Z","uid":31511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d07fc14f9d46e1a0e95c79f4ea03ee0b86dbfe9e","tid":1429194,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"大大碌<span style=\"color: red;\">鐳射槍</span>晚晚都係維港射<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幻彩詠香江（英語：A Symphony of Lights）是香港結合探射燈、雷射、LED燈等燈光效果的音樂匯演，由維多利亞港兩岸合共47座大廈摩天大樓及地標合作舉行，是香港旅遊事務署於2004年1月1日起的宣傳香港旅遊項目，歷來耗資4,400萬港元，吸引了逾400萬名旅客及市民欣賞。2005年11月21日，幻彩詠香江正式獲列入《金氏世界紀錄大全》，成為全球最大型燈光音樂匯演[1]。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港旅遊事務署</span>,拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4188f97669be32c61680c6b8816414b3f7a9594","tid":1429194,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d968a87721ab1e6a7737ecc56d93a0cfe83051e","tid":1429194,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09cdbf60566d652f63999f87afce6590e9cd267e","tid":1429194,"uid":66974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15598497aef23c236b4dbc25c966ac46dff22842","tid":1429194,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"死黑警"},{"pid":"66ef1be38ab2b65997eb3b88932948a7112790dc","tid":1429194,"uid":72507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":